modShortDescription: Adds the cut hornet from A15 (and earlier) back to the game. Spawns as an enemy animal in the forest biome. Does not spawn on horde nights.
modDescription:
Adds the cut hornet from A15 (and earlier) back to the game. Spawns as an enemy [animal](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-animals/) in the forest biome. Does not spawn on horde nights.

**[Download](https://gitlab.com/KhaineGB/khaines-modlets-a19/-/archive/master/khaines-modlets-a19-master.zip?path=KHA19-Hornet)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/19558-khaines-a19-modlets-bigger-backpacks-backpack-buttons-hp-bars-etc/).
